{"type":"message","id":"a6ddaf69","parentId":"2592ee05","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:44:49.351Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The wiki-learn cron job is calling `~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh`, but that script itself doesn't seem to call any HTTP API. Let me check what the cron job payload actually is. From the earlier cron list, the wiki-learn cron runs:\n```\n~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh\n```\n\nBut the 401 error was from a different cron job. Let me check the cron job's actual command. Looking back at the cron list:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"wiki-learn\",\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"执行 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh 并将输出追加到 ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log.md\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\nSo it runs `wiki-learn-once.sh` as an agentTurn message. The 401 error suggests the script itself or something it calls is making an HTTP request that gets a 401.\n\nBut the `wiki-learn-once.sh` script I looked at is just a bash script that manages files. It doesn't make any HTTP requests. So the 401 error might be coming from something else the script calls, or maybe the error is from a different part of the pipeline.\n\nActually, let me look more carefully at what the script does - it processes local files and writes to a log file. I need to check if there's a Python script involved that might be making HTTP calls, or if the wiki-auto-learn.py is what's actually failing.","thinkingSignature":"b7bcd100151fb4f02e2a2606e3790fdfda197de33586da2b70933084a49e2d1b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qhnzenoyr74e_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py 2>/dev/null | head -60"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":70293,"output":362,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92293,"cost":{"input":0.0210879,"output":0.0004344,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02282058}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776429878577,"responseId":"06315e36036b69aa4017673dcc63200b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d6b5f9cd","parentId":"a6ddaf69","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:44:49.749Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qhnzenoyr74e_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nLLM Wiki Auto-Learning Framework\n高鲁棒、高质量、高性能自动化学习循环\n\n基于需求 + LLM Wiki 原文设计\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nimport time\nimport subprocess\nimport re\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n# 配置\nWORKSPACE = \"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\"\nENTITIES_DIR = f\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/entities\"\nRAW_SOURCES_DIR = f\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/raw\"\nLOG_FILE = f\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/log.md\"\nARCHIVE_DIR = f\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/entities-archive\"\n\n# LLM Wiki 原文核心要点\nCORE_PRINCIPLES = {\n    \"not_rag\": \"不是RAG，是增量构建持久wiki\",\n    \"compile_once\": \"知识编译一次，持续更新\",\n    \"touch_10_15\": \"一个source触发10-15页更新\",\n    \"maintenance_zero\": \"维护成本接近零\",\n    \"human_role\": \"人负责选源、提问、思考\",\n    \"llm_role\": \"LLM负责执行维护\",\n    \"query_writeback\": \"好答案写回wiki\",\n    \"memex\": \"LLM解决维护问题\"\n}\n\nclass WikiAutoLearn:\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.stats = {\n            \"iterations\": 0,\n            \"ingested\": 0,\n            \"fixed\": 0,\n            \"queries\": 0,\n            \"errors\": 0\n        }\n        \n    def log(self, msg):\n        \"\"\"带时间戳的日志\"\"\"\n        timestamp = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")\n        print(f\"[{timestamp}] {msg}\")\n        \n    def scan_sources(self):\n        \"\"\"1. 扫描知识源 (Ingest)\"\"\"\n        sources = []\n        \n        # 扫描 docs/\n        docs_dir = Path(f\"{WORKSPACE}/docs\")\n        if docs_dir.exists():\n            for f in docs_dir.glob(\"*.md\"):\n                sources.append((\"doc\", str(f)))\n        \n        # 扫描 skills/"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":213,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nLLM Wiki Auto-Learning Framework\n高鲁棒、高质量、高性能自动化学习循环\n\n基于需求 + LLM Wiki 原文设计\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nimport time\nimport subprocess\nimport re\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n# 配置\nWORKSPACE = \"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\"\nENTITIES_DIR = f\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/entities\"\nRAW_SOURCES_DIR = f\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/raw\"\nLOG_FILE = f\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/log.md\"\nARCHIVE_DIR = f\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/entities-archive\"\n\n# LLM Wiki 原文核心要点\nCORE_PRINCIPLES = {\n    \"not_rag\": \"不是RAG，是增量构建持久wiki\",\n    \"compile_once\": \"知识编译一次，持续更新\",\n    \"touch_10_15\": \"一个source触发10-15页更新\",\n    \"maintenance_zero\": \"维护成本接近零\",\n    \"human_role\": \"人负责选源、提问、思考\",\n    \"llm_role\": \"LLM负责执行维护\",\n    \"query_writeback\": \"好答案写回wiki\",\n    \"memex\": \"LLM解决维护问题\"\n}\n\nclass WikiAutoLearn:\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.stats = {\n            \"iterations\": 0,\n            \"ingested\": 0,\n            \"fixed\": 0,\n            \"queries\": 0,\n            \"errors\": 0\n        }\n        \n    def log(self, msg):\n        \"\"\"带时间戳的日志\"\"\"\n        timestamp = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")\n        print(f\"[{timestamp}] {msg}\")\n        \n    def scan_sources(self):\n        \"\"\"1. 扫描知识源 (Ingest)\"\"\"\n        sources = []\n        \n        # 扫描 docs/\n        docs_dir = Path(f\"{WORKSPACE}/docs\")\n        if docs_dir.exists():\n            for f in docs_dir.glob(\"*.md\"):\n                sources.append((\"doc\", str(f)))\n        \n        # 扫描 skills/","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776429889686}}
{"type":"message","id":"9ff785f5","parentId":"d6b5f9cd","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:45:00.854Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The wiki-auto-learn.py script seems to be a local file-based system. It doesn't make external API calls directly. Let me check the cron job's actual error source more carefully.\n\nFrom the cron state:\n```json\n\"lastDeliveryError\": \"HTTP 401 authentication_error: login fail: Please carry the API secret key in the 'Authorization' field of the request header\"\n```\n\nThis error is about \"login fail\" and \"API secret key\". This is likely from a Feishu/Lark API call. Let me check if there's a Feishu integration.\n\nLooking at the workspace, there's a `feishu` directory. \n\nNow I'm tracing where this wiki-learn script actually runs and where the 401 error originates. The cron job executes the bash script which logs to memory/log.md, but I'm not finding Feishu API calls in that flow. Let me check the feishu extension to see if that's where the authentication failure is happening.","thinkingSignature":"21a92bc0bb68404abc7767e4d920a7861c0d26bd4fdce071c2b084b057fcb4f4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6hc3u19o5cu4_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -r \"Authorization\\|api_key\\|token\\|login\\|feishu\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py 2>/dev/null | head -10\necho \"---\"\ngrep -r \"Authorization\\|api_key\\|token\\|login\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh 2>/dev/null | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":71105,"output":293,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93036,"cost":{"input":0.0213315,"output":0.0003516,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02298138}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776429889752,"responseId":"06315e40e64439d2645f51d95a87ccad"}}
