{"type":"message","id":"49f4337c","parentId":"da177150","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:53:20.114Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the complete picture. Let me compile the comprehensive comparison and identify the gaps.\n\nKey findings:\n\n**Core ports:**\n- Gateway: 18789 (not 3100 as docs say - but docs say 18789 is the WS control UI, and 3100 is the main gateway port. The gateway is configured on 18789)\n- v8 Router 3102: **NOT RUNNING** ❌ \n- v8 Scorer 3103: ✅ RUNNING\n- v8 Classifier 3105: ✅ RUNNING\n\n**Advanced Features:**\n1. \n\nI'm checking the disabled features - Active Memory, Lobster Workflow, Context Engine, and browser automation all aren't running. Task Flow has 115 mirrored tasks but no managed ones. The three-layer memory system is partially working with ephemeral logs and session summaries from April, though MEMORY.md exists. Skills are installed at 21 in the workspace. The 3100 port isn't actually the Gateway despite the docs suggesting it should be.\n\nThe v8 Router on 3102 was described in documentation but never actually deployed, and the v8 Router reference in session-summary hook has been updated to use the codingplan API instead. Gateway is running v2026.4.15, newer than the documented v2026.4.14.","thinkingSignature":"0de5b9a13af581bc2b3720d57efde1009d2c850dc4e486688d0c68729313b30d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n现在全面对比完成。逐项核查结果：\n\n---\n\n## 📊 全面对比：当前系统 vs v2026.4.14\n\n### 🔴 P0 - 核心断链\n\n| 功能 | 文档描述 | 实际情况 | 状态 |\n|------|----------|----------|------|\n| **v8 Router (3102)** | Gateway进程内，微服务路由 | **不存在** | ❌ 文档架构从未部署 |\n| **Gateway 端口** | 文档说3100，18789是Control UI | 实际 Gateway = 18789，3100是第三方服务 | ⚠️ 端口定义与文档不符 |\n| **Active Memory** | 阻塞式主动记忆插件 | `disabled` | ❌ |\n| **Lobster 工作流** | DSL runtime，typed workflow | `disabled` | ❌ |\n| **Context Engine** | 可插拔上下文引擎 | 未安装 lossless-claw | ❌ |\n| **Browser 自动化** | Edge CDP + portproxy | browser插件loaded但**无Edge运行** | ❌ |\n\n### 🟡 P1 - 功能未激活\n\n| 功能 | 文档描述 | 实际情况 | 状态 |\n|------|----------|----------|------|\n| **Task Flow Managed** | 托管编排任务 | 115个任务全是 `mirrored`（外部观察），0个 managed | ⚠️ |\n| **session-summary hook** | /new时LLM生成摘要 | **handler已修复**（改用codingplan），待验证 | ⏳ |\n| **羊毛系统** | ClawHub市场 | 已安装21个skills，2363行entities | ✅ |\n\n### ✅ 已修复/正常\n\n| 功能 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| v8 Scorer (3103) | ✅ |\n| v8 Classifier (3105) | ✅ |\n| wiki-learn cron | ✅ 刚修复401 |\n| 三层记忆（瞬时层） | ✅ ephemeral实时写入 |\n| 三层记忆（会话层） | ✅ session-summary hook已改 |\n| 三层记忆（长期层） | ✅ MEMORY.md存在 |\n| memory-maintain cron | ✅ ok |\n| memory-keeper cron | ✅ ok |\n| summary-pruner cron | ✅ enabled |\n| ACPX Runtime | ✅ loaded（Codex/Claude Code支持）|\n\n---\n\n## 结论：没有全面跑通\n\n**4个核心高级功能完全未启用**：\n1. Active Memory（主动记忆）\n2. Lobster（typed workflow）\n3. Context Engine（可插拔上下文）\n4. Browser 自动化\n\n**根本原因**：文档描述的是\"完整功能框架\"，但实际部署时这些功能以 **plugin 形式** 提供，需要手动 `openclaw plugins install` 并配置才能启用。当前系统只跑了最基础的消息收发 + 评分分类链路。\n\n要继续激活这些功能吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":50326,"output":869,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72833,"cost":{"input":0.0150978,"output":0.0010428,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.017438879999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776430373249,"responseId":"06316025fd70a4c3f55757adeb3187c2"}}
