{"type":"message","id":"562ef230","parentId":"c16b3518","timestamp":"2026-04-17T13:02:17.517Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Active Memory ✅ and Lobster ✅ are now loaded. Now I need to handle Context Engine and Browser automation.\n\n**Context Engine** - I need to find what's providing this. The document mentions \"lossless-claw\" or a context engine plugin. Let me check what provides this functionality.\n\n**Browser automation** - The browser plugin is loaded. But Edge CDP isn't running. For Windows WSL, the document describes:\n- Windows Edge --remote-debugging-port=9222\n- netsh portproxy (9222 → 19222)\n- WSL Playwright CDP connects to localhost:19222\n\nThe browser plugin needs Edge running with remote debugging enabled. Let me check if Edge is available on Windows side, and set up the portproxy.\n\n\nI'll tackle Context Engine first by searching through the codebase to identify what plugin or module provides that functionality.","thinkingSignature":"499e154fd2b3b3dd9ad0bcf02627d1f7b602ff5901387385eded92b93b0416f2"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ Active Memory + Lobster 已加载。\n\n第2步——查找 Context Engine 实现：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ho52el1cqcog_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/openclaw.mjs plugins list 2>&1 | grep -iE \"context|engine|lossless\" | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":44333,"output":259,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66230,"cost":{"input":0.0132999,"output":0.00031079999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01490898}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776430928306,"responseId":"0631624f5546b27240ed365c681051a5"}}
