{"type":"message","id":"65ac2f0c","parentId":"9f32fd30","timestamp":"2026-04-17T14:21:00.491Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"v8 Scorer returned a suspicious all-zeros score with max:18. That seems wrong for a task. And the classifier returned \"clarify\" which is also odd for \"测试消息\". Let me investigate further.Also, the classifier returned a non-standard response format - it has `response` field, `scene`, `confidence` etc. but it looks like it's giving an LLM response instead of structured classification. This might mean the classifier is not properly configured or is just running an LLM to do classification.Let me check the listener config next.","thinkingSignature":"6ca727b2bfd9bc8e0f8ff51fb09465ce1a8f752f0094fcfeb0ba29b2747494ac"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kgmmrwl74uqe_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 3. Listener 配置验证 ===\"\ncat /home/ai/openclaw-listener/config.json 2>/dev/null | python3 -m json.tool\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 4. Active Memory 配置 ===\"\ncat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | python3 -c \"\nimport json,sys\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\nam = d.get('plugins',{}).get('entries',{}).get('active-memory',{})\nprint(json.dumps(am, indent=2))\n\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 5. auth-profiles minimax ===\"\ncat ~/.openclaw/auth-profiles.json | python3 -c \"\nimport json,sys\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\nk = d['profiles'].get('minimax:cn',{})\nprint(f'type={k.get(\\\"type\\\")}, key=****{k.get(\\\"key\\\",\\\"\\\")[-8:]}')\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":61107,"output":330,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83075,"cost":{"input":0.0183321,"output":0.000396,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02002638}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776435651241,"responseId":"063174c29e6c2c6855a01126f2749e7b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a859f8ab","parentId":"65ac2f0c","timestamp":"2026-04-17T14:21:00.908Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_kgmmrwl74uqe_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 3. Listener 配置验证 ===\n{\n    \"gateway\": {\n        \"url\": \"ws://127.0.0.1:18789\",\n        \"token\": \"0da4fe1cb845fc8386105026ee6b941b288a2a4264a16ced\",\n        \"heartbeatInterval\": 30000,\n        \"reconnect\": {\n            \"initialDelay\": 1000,\n            \"maxDelay\": 60000,\n            \"factor\": 1.5\n        }\n    },\n    \"api\": {\n        \"intent\": \"http://localhost:3103/api/score\",\n        \"score\": \"http://localhost:3103/api/score\",\n        \"timeout\": 5000,\n        \"retries\": 3,\n        \"retryDelay\": 1000\n    },\n    \"reply\": {\n        \"enabled\": false,\n        \"template\": \"\\ud83e\\udd16 \\u610f\\u56fe\\uff1a{{intent}}\\uff0c\\u8bc4\\u5206\\uff1a{{score}}\"\n    },\n    \"behavior\": {\n        \"messageField\": \"content\",\n        \"queueEnabled\": true,\n        \"queueDbPath\": \"/tmp/openclaw-listener-queue.db\",\n        \"batchSize\": 10,\n        \"batchIntervalMs\": 100\n    },\n    \"health\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"port\": 3106,\n        \"endpoint\": \"/health\"\n    },\n    \"logging\": {\n        \"level\": \"info\",\n        \"file\": \"/tmp/openclaw-listener.log\"\n    }\n}\n\n=== 4. Active Memory 配置 ===\n{\n  \"enabled\": true\n}\n\n=== 5. auth-profiles minimax ===\ntype=api_key, key=****T2kKZ_Ls"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":209,"aggregated":"=== 3. Listener 配置验证 ===\n{\n    \"gateway\": {\n        \"url\": \"ws://127.0.0.1:18789\",\n        \"token\": \"0da4fe1cb845fc8386105026ee6b941b288a2a4264a16ced\",\n        \"heartbeatInterval\": 30000,\n        \"reconnect\": {\n            \"initialDelay\": 1000,\n            \"maxDelay\": 60000,\n            \"factor\": 1.5\n        }\n    },\n    \"api\": {\n        \"intent