{"type":"message","id":"24107eeb","parentId":"46725096","timestamp":"2026-04-17T14:21:58.849Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The gateway ws config is empty, so no explicit WebSocket timeout settings. The gateway is in \"local\" mode with token auth.\n\nThe listener reconnect loop seems to be an architectural issue rather than a configuration problem. The gateway might be closing connections due to some internal logic. Since the listener reconnects successfully, it's not a critical failure - but it's inefficient.\n\nLet me now check the auto-score-classify hook to see if it's actually working (it writes to session state files).\n\nActually, let me step back and give the user the critical issues I've found. The biggest issues are:\n\n1. **Listener WebSocket reconnect loop** - gateway closing connection every 10s → listener keeps reconnecting → inefficient but functional\n\n\n2. **Active Memory runs on every message** - with no bounds configured, this could tank performance\n3. **v8 Scorer returns all-zeros** - for simple inputs it scores 0, which seems wrong\n4. **v8 Classifier returns LLM-style response** - not the structured format the docs promise\n5. **3100 port unknown** - listening but not associated with any known service\n\nLet me verify the auto-score-classify hook is actually functioning by checking if it's writing to the session state directory.","thinkingSignature":"4595348222e500280065bd2812cf244f3f84ba592ce1a52fc342f10ae258fdc1"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i7huiq00ale0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 12. auto-score-classify 输出验证 ===\"\nls ~/.openclaw/sessions/ 2>/dev/null | head -5\necho \"---\"\nfind ~/.openclaw/sessions/ -name \"*.json\" -newer ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/ephemeral/2026-04-17-13.jsonl 2>/dev/null | head -5\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 13. session-summary hook 配置检查 ===\"\ncat ~/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary/HOOK.md 2>/dev/null | head -30\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 14. context-hook.js 检查 ===\"\ncat ~/.openclaw/hooks/context-hook.js 2>/dev/null | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":64653,"output":430,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86721,"cost":{"input":0.0193959,"output":0.000516,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02121018}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776435705466,"responseId":"063174f9cde521ef80b70ee08e839a94"}}
{"type":"message","id":"391cefdf","parentId":"24107eeb","timestamp":"2026-04-17T14:21:59.426Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_i7huiq00ale0_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 12. auto-score-classify 输出验证 ===\nagent:coder:main\nagent:fast_agent:feishu:group:oc_1b955e738aa196d7f2afe9e1c1d35575\nagent:fast_agent:main\nagent:main:main\n---\n/home/ai/.openclaw/sessions/agent:main:main/context.json\n\n=== 13. session-summary hook 配置检查 ===\n---\nname: session-summary\ndescription: \"session 结束时（/new 或 /reset）生成结构化摘要，写入 memory/，供下次 bootstrap 读取。依赖 context.previousSessionEntry.sessionFile 读取刚结束的 session 内容。\"\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\": {\n      \"emoji\": \"📝\",\n      \"events\": [\"command:new\", \"command:reset\"],\n      \"requires\": {\n        \"bins\": [\"node\"],\n        \"config\": [\"workspace.dir\"]\n      },\n      \"always\": true\n    }\n  }\n---\n\n# session-summary\n\n每次 `/new` 或 `/reset` 触发时，异步生成刚结束 session 的结构化摘要。\n\n## 行为\n\n- **异步执行**：hook 立即返回，摘要生成在后台，不阻塞命令响应\n- **降级策略**：LLM 不可用或生成失败时，写入规则摘要，不报错不中断\n- **文件格式**：`memory/YYYY-MM-DD-{slug}.md`，带 `<!-- summary-only -->` 标记\n\n## 摘要格式\n\n```markdown\n\n=== 14. context-hook.js 检查 ===\n/**\n * Context Hook for OpenClaw\n * \n * 监听消息事件，自动调用保护层context模块\n * \n * 支持的事件:\n * - message:receive: 用户发送消息\n * - message:send: AI 发送消息\n * - agent:response: Agent 回复\n */\n\nconst handler = async (event) => {\n  try {\n    // 检查是否有全局上下文接口\n    if (!global.openclaw || !global.openclaw.addContextMessage) {\n      // 尝试加载保护层\n      try {\n        const protection = await import(process.env.HOME + '/.openclaw/protection/index.js');\n        await protection.default.init();\n      } catch (e) {\n        console.log('[ContextHook] 保护层未加载，跳过');\n        return;\n      }\n    }\n\n    // 处理用户消息\n    if (event.type === 'message' || event.type === 'message:receive') {\n      const content = event.message?.content || event.content || '';\n      if (content) {\n        global.openclaw?.addContextMessage('user', content, event.taskId);"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":291,"aggregated":"=== 12. auto-score-classify 输出验证 ===\nagent:coder:main\nagent:fast_agent:feishu:group:oc_1b955e738aa196d7f2afe9e1c1d35575\nagent:fast_agent:main\nagent:main:main\n---\n/home/ai/.openclaw/sessions/agent:main:main/context.json\n\n=== 13. session-summary hook 配置检查 ===\n---\nname: session-summary\ndescription: \"session 结束时（/new 或 /reset）生成结构化摘要，写入 memory/，供下次 bootstrap 读取。依赖 context.previousSessionEntry.sessionFile 读取刚结束的 session 内容。\"\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\": {\n      \"emoji\": \"📝\",\n      \"events\": [\"command:new\", \"command:reset\"],\n      \"requires\": {\n        \"bins\": [\"node\"],\n        \"config\": [\"workspace.dir\"]\n      },\n      \"always\": true\n    }\n  }\n---\n\n# session-summary\n\n每次 `/new` 或 `/reset` 触发时，异步生成刚结束 session 的结构化摘要。\n\n## 行为\n\n- **异步执行**：hook 立即返回，摘要生成在后台，不阻塞命令响应\n- **降级策略**：LLM 不可用或生成失败时，写入规则摘要，不报错不中断\n- **文件格式**：`memory/YYYY-MM-DD-{slug}.md`，带 `<!-- summary-only -->` 标记\n\n## 摘要格式\n\n```markdown\n\n=== 14. context-hook.js 检查 ===\n/**\n * Context Hook for OpenClaw\n * \n * 监听消息事件，自动调用保护层context模块\n * \n * 支持的事件:\n * - message:receive: 用户发送消息\n * - message:send: AI 发送消息\n * - agent:response: Agent 回复\n */\n\nconst handler = async (event) => {\n  try {\n    // 检查是否有全局上下文接口\n    if (!global.openclaw || !global.openclaw.addContextMessage) {\n      // 尝试加载保护层\n      try {\n        const protection = await import(process.env.HOME + '/.openclaw/protection/index.js');\n        await protection.default.init();\n      } catch (e) {\n        console.log('[ContextHook] 保护层未加载，跳过');\n        return;\n      }\n    }\n\n    // 处理用户消息\n    if (event.type === 'message' || event.type === 'message:receive') {\n      const content = event.message?.content || event.content || '';\n      if (content) {\n        global.openclaw?.addContextMessage('user', content, event.taskId);","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776435719335}}
{"type":"message","id":"624ee980","parentId":"391cefdf","timestamp":"2026-04-17T14:22:11.228Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see more context. The context-hook.js is trying to import a protection module that may not exist. Let me check if the protection module exists.Let me also check the session state file to see if auto-score-classify is actually writing scores.Let me now compile the critical issues found:\n\n1. **Listener reconnect loop** - The gateway is closing the WebSocket every 10 seconds. This is the #1 issue. The listener keeps reconnecting.\n\n2. **Active Memory runs unbounded** - With only `enabled: true` and no query limits, it runs on every eligible message\n\n3. **context-hook.js trying to load non-existent protection module** - This might generate errors but is caught gracefully\n   \n4. **v8 Scorer and Classifier returning unusual responses** - The scorer shows all zeros for basic inputs, while the classifier appears to generate LLM-style text rather than structured data\n\n5. **Unknown 3100 port** - This needs investigation as it could be a security concern\n\nI should also verify whether the protection module is actually missing and test the v8 Scorer with more complex inputs to see if it produces meaningful scores.","thinkingSignature":"2215f0f7d5730bd7bf17463fcfc7071ab62dbf4df9cadb92f96b13c7e1951b4d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_y9oke8z69zu0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 15. Protection 模块检查 ===\"\nls ~/.openclaw/protection/ 2>/dev/null || echo \"protection 目录不存在\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 16. v8 Scorer 复杂输入测试 ===\"\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:3103/api/score \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"text\":\"我需要你分析这个项目的所有代码文件，重构核心模块，并编写完整的测试用例，然后部署到生产环境\"}' 2>&1\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 17. Listener 最近日志（最后10条）===\"\ntail -10 /tmp/openclaw-listener.log 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"\nimport sys,json\nfor line in sys.stdin:\n    try:\n        d=json.