{"type":"message","id":"0a6628b2","parentId":"46506b9a","timestamp":"2026-04-17T14:23:08.361Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can't easily determine what 3100 is. Let me try a different approach - checking if it's related to Docker, WSL, or some other system service.\n\nActually, the most important thing to focus on is fixing the actual issues. Let me now synthesize and fix:\n\n1. **Listener reconnect loop** - This seems to be the gateway closing the connection due to idle timeout. The listener reconnects fine. The question is whether this is causing any message loss. Since the queue is persistent, messages should be replayed.\n\n2. **Active Memory runs on every message** - This should have a queryMode or similar setting to limit when it runs.\n\n3. **The 3100 port** - not critical to identify right now.\n\n\nLet me verify the ephemeral writes are happening correctly for the current session and double-check the context-hook.js for any errors. The real question is whether the listener's 10-second reconnect loop is actually problematic or just expected gateway behavior. I should trace through what happens when the gateway closes the WebSocket to understand if the listener's reconnection logic is handling it properly.\n\nThe flow shows the gateway closes the connection cleanly, the listener's close handler fires and logs the event, then schedules a reconnect. Since the queue is persistent and the listener replays messages on reconnect, messages shouldn't be lost even if the gateway is enforcing a strict idle timeout on its end.\n\nThis looks like the gateway's WebSocket implementation has a built-in 10-second idle timeout that's closing connections, which isn't something I can fix without adjusting the gateway's configuration or code. Let me focus on what I can actually resolve.","thinkingSignature":"603e4cdaca816b9c48de9a2171a85204a7dccde711fcdc27d0bd409c9e5ec23f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rtcby3xijb8i_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 24. Active Memory 日志（最近错误）===\"\njournalctl --user -u openclaw-gateway.service -n 50 2>/dev/null | grep -iE \"active.memory|active-memory\" | tail -10\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 25. v8 Classifier classifer 输出结构验证 ===\"\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:3105/classify \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"text\":\"帮我写一个Python脚本处理文件\"}' 2>&1 | python3 -c \"\nimport sys,json\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\nprint('scene:', d.get('scene'))\nprint('confidence:', d.get('confidence'))\nprint('response:', d.get('response','')[:100] if d.get('response') else 'N/A')\n\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 26. 检查当前系统负载 ===\"\nuptime\necho \"---\"\nfree -m | awk 'NR==2{print \"内存: \"$3\"M used / \"$2\"M total\"}'"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":68740,"output":574,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90952,"cost":{"input":0.020621999999999998,"output":0.0006887999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.022609079999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776435773804,"responseId":"0631753c8ba00c55482b307c6a79b58d"}}
