{"type":"message","id":"4ce9f6f6","parentId":"b0356810","timestamp":"2026-04-17T14:23:25.521Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a complete picture. Let me compile the critical findings:\n\n**Critical Issues:**\n\n1. **Listener WebSocket reconnect loop** — Gateway (153280) closes the WebSocket every ~10 seconds (code 1000, clean close). Listener (149465) reconnects immediately. This is a constant loop. The cause: gateway enforces a 10s idle timeout on WebSocket connections. The listener's heartbeat fires every 30s, but the connection closes before that. The queue database should survive reconnections, but this is inefficient and could cause message loss if the gateway closes mid-message. **FIX**: Need to reduce the gateway's idle timeout or the listener needs to send something more frequently.\n   \nThe v8 Classifier is returning an LLM response instead of a proper structured scene label, which doesn't match the spec at all. And Active Memory is enabled but running with default settings on every message, which will tank performance. I need to check the actual spec for the Classifier to understand what the correct response format should be.\n\nLooking at the spec more carefully, the scene-classifier at 3105 should return `{scene, confidence, meta}` but instead it's giving me an LLM-generated response wrapped in an oddly structured format with `response`, `intercepted`, `scene`, and `meta` fields. This looks like the scene-classifier is actually an LLM wrapper that's doing classification through an LLM call, not a proper ML classifier.\n\nThe 3100 port is also suspicious—it's listening on all interfaces but I can't identify what process owns it, which is a potential security concern I need to investigate further.\n\nThe real priority though is fixing the listener's WebSocket reconnection loop and the classifier response format, since those are actively broken.","thinkingSignature":"79eec67a7a3419a1c25824044fa80ea1181009bfc671f04b733479c6f4e27d1e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7nauzsu8pvso_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 27. scene-classifier 源码分析 ===\"\ncat /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/scene-classifier/app.py 2>/dev/null | head -60\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 28. 3100 端口安全检查 ===\"\nss -tlnp | grep 3100\ncurl -s --connect-timeout 2 http://localhost:3100/ 2>/dev/null | head -5 || echo \"无HTTP响应\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":69447,"output":479,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91564,"cost":{"input":0.020834099999999998,"output":0.0005748,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.022707179999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776435788923,"responseId":"0631754ca56b1964123e4c81615ed7fa"}}
