{"type":"message","id":"2754421d","parentId":"f7977fb6","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:09:51.431Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-04-18 00:09 GMT+8] 是这个吗：\n\n### 六因子定义\n\n| 因子 | 分值范围 | 说明 | 典型触发词/模式 |\n|------|----------|------|----------------|\n| **logic** | 0-3 | 逻辑复杂度：衡量代码分支、重构、算法、多文件关联的复杂程度 | `重构`、`refactor`、`算法`、`递归`、`正则`、`状态机`、`多个文件` |\n| **risk** | 0-3 | 风险度：操作可能造成的破坏性，尤其是数据删除、系统配置变更、生产环境影响 | `rm -rf`、`删除`、`数据库`、`chmod`、`sudo`、`生产环境`、`清空` |\n| **duration** | 0-3 | 预估时长：任务中耗时较长的操作，如编译、安装依赖、运行测试、下载 | `编译`、`构建`、`npm install`、`测试`、`下载`、`打包` |\n| **resource** | 0-3 | 资源消耗：任务对 CPU、内存、GPU 或 I/O 的占用程度 | `训练`、`模型`、`GPU`、`视频处理`、`大数据`、`并发`、`多线程` |\n| **uncertainty** | 0-3 | 不确定性：涉及外部 API 调用、网络请求、调试等不可控因素 | `API`、`curl`、`网络请求`、`第三方`、`调试`、`可能`、`尝试` |\n| **dependency** | 0-3 | 依赖复杂度：项目或任务的模块耦合度，如 monorepo、微服务、多依赖 | `monorepo`、`微服务`、`多包`、`依赖关系`、`workspace`、`子模块` |\n\n### 评分流程\n\n1. **原始分计算**：每个因子独立评分（0-3），总原始分范围 0-18。\n2. **归一化**：采用平方根公式将原始分映射到 0-100：\n ```\n normalized = round(sqrt(rawScore / 18) * 100)\n ```\n *效果：低分增长快，高分增长缓，更符合实际复杂度分布。*\n\n### 策略选择\n\n基于归一化分数和特殊规则（如 `risk >= 3` 强制隔离）选择执行策略：\n\n| 归一化分 | 策略 | 超时 |\n|----------|------|------|\n| ≤20 | `DIRECT` | 30s |\n| 21-40 | `STEP_ARCHIVE` | 60s |\n| 41-60 | `SPAWN_SUBAGENT` | 120s |\n| 61-80 | `PARALLEL_SHARDS` | 240s |\n| >80 | `MEGA_TASK` | 7200s |\n\n**特殊规则（优先级从高到低）**：\n1. `risk >= 3` → `SPAWN_SUBAGENT` (180s)\n2. `resource >= 3` → `PARALLEL_SHARDS` (300s)\n3. `uncertainty >= 3` → `SPAWN_SUBAGENT` (180s)\n4. `duration >= 3 && dependency >= 2` → `MEGA_TASK` (7200s)\n5. `logic >= 3 && duration >= 3` → `PARALLEL_SHARDS` (300s)\n\n### 上下文增强\n\n可通过 `context` 参数传递额外信息，动态提升因子分数（上限均为 3）：\n\n| 条件 | 增强效果 |\n|------|----------|\n| `context.fileCount > 10` | `logic` +2 |\n| `context.estimatedLines > 1000` | `duration` +2 |\n| `context.isProduction === true` | `risk` +2 |"}],"timestamp":1776442191377}}
{"type":"message","id":"9736050e","parentId":"2754421d","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:09:56.292Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if the v8.0 scoring engine has the \"context enhancement\" feature - the ability to dynamically boost factor scores based on context parameters like `fileCount`, `estimatedLines`, `isProduction`. Let me check if this feature exists in the actual v8.0 scoring.js code.","thinkingSignature":"702e1d3a44fd72a0db07c72712a12279f069f466ef9901b3488e18d26bb319fd"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q7jwlva6z7z4_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -A 30 \"context\\.\\|fileCount\\|isProduction\\|estimatedLines\\|上下文\" /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/scoring.js 2>/dev/null | head -60"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":132,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":80016,"totalTokens":101844,"cost":{"input":0.0000174,"output":0.0001584,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0.030006,"total":0.03148008}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776442191492,"responseId":"06318e4ed3b4cee7821790483ab1fffd"}}
{"type":"message","id":"312ca8e2","parentId":"9736050e","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:09:56.760Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_q7jwlva6z7z4_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// 上下文增强\n if (factorDef === FACTOR_DEFINITIONS.logic && context.fileCount > 10) {\n score = Math.max(score, 2);\n }\n if (factorDef === FACTOR_DEFINITIONS.duration && context.estimatedLines > 1000) {\n score = Math.max(score, 2);\n }\n if (factorDef === FACTOR_DEFINITIONS.risk && context.isProduction) {\n score = Math.max(score, 2);\n }\n\n return Math.min(score, factorDef.max);\n}\n\n/**\n * 平方根归一化：原始分数 (0-18) → 0-100\n * 曲线特点：低分增长快，高分增长缓，更符合实际分布\n */\nfunction normalizeScore(rawScore) {\n // rawScore 范围 0-18\n // 公式：sqrt(rawScore / 18) * 100\n // 0→0, 2→33, 3→41, 6→57, 9→70, 12→81, 18→100\n const normalized = Math.round(Math.sqrt(rawScore / 18) * 100);\n return Math.min(100, normalized);\n}\n\n/**\n * 策略选择 (基于归一化分数和特殊规则)\n */\nfunction selectStrategy(normalizedScore, factors) {\n // 特殊规则 1：高风险强制隔离执行\n if (factors.risk >= 3) {\n return { strategy: 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT', timeout: 180 };\n }\n\n // 特殊规则 2：高资源消耗强制并行分片\n if (factors.resource >= 3) {\n return { strategy: 'PARALLEL_SHARDS', timeout: 300 };\n--\n * @param {Object} context - 可选的上下文信息 (fileCount, estimatedLines, isProduction)\n * @returns {Object} { score, factors, recommendedStrategy, timeout }\n */\nfunction scoreTask(prompt, context = {}) {\n const text = prompt || '';\n const factors = {};\n let rawTotal = 0;\n\n // 计算各因子原始分数\n for (const [name, def] of Object.entries(FACTOR_DEFINITIONS)) {\n const factorScore = calculateFactorScore(text, context, def);\n factors[name] = factorScore;\n rawTotal += factorScore;\n }\n\n // 归一化到 0-100\n const normalizedScore = normalizeScore(rawTotal);\n\n // 选择策略和超时\n const { strategy, timeout } = selectStrategy(normalizedScore, factors);"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":266,"aggregated":"// 上下文增强\n if (factorDef === FACTOR_DEFINITIONS.logic && context.fileCount > 10) {\n score = Math.max(score, 2);\n }\n if (factorDef === FACTOR_DEFINITIONS.duration && context.estimatedLines > 1000) {\n score = Math.max(score, 2);\n }\n if (factorDef === FACTOR_DEFINITIONS.risk && context.isProduction) {\n score = Math.max(score, 2);\n }\n\n return Math.min(score, factorDef.max);\n}\n\n/**\n * 平方根归一化：原始分数 (0-18) → 0-100\n * 曲线特点：低分增长快，高分增长缓，更符合实际分布\n */\nfunction normalizeScore(rawScore) {\n // rawScore 范围 0-18\n // 公式：sqrt(rawScore / 18) * 100\n // 0→0, 2→33, 3→41, 6→57, 9→70, 12→81, 18→100\n const normalized = Math.round(Math.sqrt(rawScore / 18) * 100);\n return Math.min(100, normalized);\n}\n\n/**\n * 策略选择 (基于归一化分数和特殊规则)\n */\nfunction selectStrategy(normalizedScore, factors) {\n // 特殊规则 1：高风险强制隔离执行\n if (factors.risk >= 3) {\n return { strategy: 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT', timeout: 180 };\n }\n\n // 特殊规则 2：高资源消耗强制并行分片\n if (factors.resource >= 3) {\n return { strategy: 'PARALLEL_SHARDS', timeout: 300 };\n--\n * @param {Object} context - 可选的上下文信息 (fileCount, estimatedLines, isProduction)\n * @returns {Object} { score, factors, recommendedStrategy, timeout }\n */\nfunction scoreTask(prompt, context = {}) {\n const text = prompt || '';\n const factors = {};\n let rawTotal = 0;\n\n // 计算各因子原始分数\n for (const [name, def] of Object.entries(FACTOR_DEFINITIONS)) {\n const factorScore = calculateFactorScore(text, context, def);\n factors[name] = factorScore;\n rawTotal += factorScore;\n }\n\n // 归一化到 0-100\n const normalizedScore = normalizeScore(rawTotal);\n\n // 选择策略和超时\n const { strategy, timeout } = selectStrategy(normalizedScore, factors);","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776442196688}}
