{"type":"message","id":"59d97b41","parentId":"06e258e6","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:15:43.364Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about Context Management - which was one of the areas where I found gaps in the deep comparison. Specifically:\n\n1. Context Engine - partial implementation (only ContextProtector, not the full pluggable architecture)\n2. No Usage Tracking configured\n3. Compaction only has mode \"safeguard\"\n\nLet me dig deeper into the actual Context Engine implementation to give a precise answer about what's implemented vs what's missing.","thinkingSignature":"19e5523d5ce5eb3b75d75a41aceebd6f56fd94c7731b1d3ae6f29a7b53c72588"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_le21svv75fdo_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== Context Engine 源码结构 ===\"\nfind ~/.openclaw/v8/src/context/ -type f -name \"*.js\" 2>/dev/null | head -20\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Context 入口 ===\"\ncat ~/.openclaw/v8/src/context/ContextProtector.js 2>/dev/null\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 实际上下文组装 ===\"\ngrep -r \"assemble\\|context.*assemble\\|buildContext\\|buildPrompt\" ~/.openclaw/v8/src/ 2>/dev/null | grep -v \".js.map\" | grep -v \"node_modules\" | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":239,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":89083,"totalTokens":111018,"cost":{"input":0.0000174,"output":0.0002868,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0.033406125,"total":0.035008605}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776442532627,"responseId":"06318fa4eead017534c4a985663c0610"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8b5f8529","parentId":"59d97b41","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:15:43.826Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_le21svv75fdo_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== Context Engine 源码结构 ===\n/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/context/ContextProtector.js\n\n=== Context 入口 ===\nconst EventEmitter = require('events');\n\nclass ContextProtector extends EventEmitter {\n  constructor(config) {\n    super();\n    this.maxTokens = config.context.maxContextTokens || 128000;\n    this.summarizeThreshold = config.context.summarizeThreshold || 0.8;\n    this.chunkSize = config.context.chunkSize || 4096;\n  }\n\n  estimateTokens(text) {\n    return Math.ceil(text.length / 4);\n  }\n\n  async protectContext(messages, newMessage) {\n    const fullContext = [...messages, newMessage];\n    let totalText = fullContext.map(m => m.content).join('\\n');\n    let tokenCount = this.estimateTokens(totalText);\n\n    if (tokenCount > this.maxTokens * this.summarizeThreshold) {\n      this.emit('summarize:triggered', { tokenCount, threshold: this.maxTokens });\n      const systemMessages = messages.filter(m => m.role === 'system');\n      const recentMessages = messages.slice(-5);\n      const summary = await this._summarize(messages.slice(0, -5));\n      const compressed = [\n        ...systemMessages,\n        { role: 'assistant', content: `[Previous conversation summary: ${summary}]` },\n        ...recentMessages,\n        newMessage\n      ];\n      totalText = compressed.map(m => m.content).join('\\n');\n      tokenCount = this.estimateTokens(totalText);\n      return { messages: compressed, tokenCount, summarized: true };\n    }\n\n    return { messages: fullContext, tokenCount, summarized: false };\n  }\n\n  async _summarize(messages) {\n    const text = messages.map(m => `${m.role}: ${m.content}`).join('\\n');\n    if (text.length > 2000) {\n      return text.substring(0, 2000) + '...';\n    }\n    return text;\n  }\n\n  async readFileInChunks(filePath) {\n    const fs = require('fs').promises;\n    const stats = await fs.stat(filePath);\n    const chunks = [];\n    let bytesRead = 0;\n    const fd = await fs.open(filePath, 'r');\n    const buffer = Buffer.alloc(this.chunkSize);\n    while (bytesRead < stats.size) {\n      const { bytesRead: read } = await fd.read(buffer, 0, this.chunkSize, bytesRead);\n      if (read === 0) break;\n      chunks.push(buffer.slice(0, read).toString('utf8'));\n      bytesRead += read;\n    }\n    await fd.close();\n    return chunks.join('');\n  }\n}\n\nmodule.exports = { ContextProtector };\n\n=== 实际上下文组装 ==="}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":256,"aggregated":"=== Context Engine 源码结构 ===\n/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/context/ContextProtector.js\n\n=== Context 入口 ===\nconst EventEmitter = require('events');\n\nclass ContextProtector extends EventEmitter {\n  constructor(config) {\n    super();\n    this.maxTokens = config.context.maxContextTokens || 128000;\n    this.summarizeThreshold = config.context.summarizeThreshold || 0.8;\n    this.chunkSize = config.context.chunkSize || 4096;\n  }\n\n  estimateTokens(text) {\n    return Math.ceil(text.length / 4);\n  }\n\n  async protectContext(messages, newMessage) {\n    const fullContext = [...messages, newMessage];\n    let totalText = fullContext.map(m => m.content).join('\\n');\n    let tokenCount = this.estimateTokens(totalText);\n\n    if (tokenCount > this.maxTokens * this.summarizeThreshold) {\n      this.emit('summarize:triggered', { tokenCount, threshold: this.maxTokens });\n      const systemMessages = messages.filter(m => m.role === 'system');\n      const recentMessages = messages.slice(-5);\n      const summary = await this._summarize(messages.slice(0, -5));\n      const compressed = [\n        ...systemMessages,\n        { role: 'assistant', content: `[Previous conversation summary: ${summary}]` },\n        ...recentMessages,\n        newMessage\n      ];\n      totalText = compressed.map(m => m.content).join('\\n');\n      tokenCount = this.estimateTokens(totalText);\n      return { messages: compressed, tokenCount, summarized: true };\n    }\n\n    return { messages: fullContext, tokenCount, summarized: false };\n  }\n\n  async _summarize(messages) {\n    const text = messages.map(m => `${m.role}: ${m.content}`).join('\\n');\n    if (text.length > 2000) {\n      return text.substring(0, 2000) + '...';\n    }\n    return text;\n  }\n\n  async readFileInChunks(filePath) {\n    const fs = require('fs').promises;\n    const stats = await fs.stat(filePath);\n    const chunks = [];\n    let bytesRead = 0;\n    const fd = await fs.open(filePath, 'r');\n    const buffer = Buffer.alloc(this.chunkSize);\n    while (bytesRead < stats.size) {\n      const { bytesRead: read } = await fd.read(buffer, 0, this.chunkSize, bytesRead);\n      if (read === 0) break;\n      chunks.push(buffer.slice(0, read).toString('utf8'));\n      bytesRead += read;\n    }\n    await fd.close();\n    return chunks.join('');\n  }\n}\n\nmodule.exports = { ContextProtector };\n\n=== 实际上下文组装 ===","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776442543759}}
{"type":"message","id":"30ce3e87","parentId":"8b5f8529","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:15:48.527Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the actual Context Engine implementation. Let me check the protection module too.","thinkingSignature":"b0bf9c188f396dd48658dfb9840e4a0e05d8c7e88f9368038a7b7cf81882099e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_011nnd1xy0tv_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== Protection 模块 ===\"\nhead -50 ~/.openclaw/protection/context_protector.js 2>/dev/null\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Protection middleware ===\"\ngrep -A 5 \"assemble\\|context.*build\\|protectContext\" ~/.openclaw/protection/middleware.js 2>/dev/null | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":89978,"output":110,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111726,"cost":{"input":0.026993399999999997,"output":0.00013199999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.028423679999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776442543831,"responseId":"06318fae975d96c1363faa2b43427b8e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0f31a3b5","parentId":"30ce3e87","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:15:48.923Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_011nnd1xy0tv_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== Protection 模块 ===\n/**\n * OpenCLaw 保护层 - 上下文保护模块 (context_protector.js)\n * \n * 功能：\n * - 多维度检测（消息数+字符数+Token使用率）\n * - 自动压缩（API优先，降级裁剪）\n * - 定期轮询底层检测\n * - 回滚机制\n */\n\nimport * as fs from 'fs';\nimport * as path from 'path';\nimport * as os from 'os';\n\nclass ContextProtector {\n  constructor(options = {}) {\n    this.msgThreshold = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_MSG_THRESHOLD || '50');\n    this.charThreshold = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_CHAR_THRESHOLD || '102400'); // 100KB\n    this.tokenRatioThreshold = parseFloat(process.env.OPENCLAW_TOKEN_RATIO || '0.8');\n    this.tokenLimit = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_TOKEN_LIMIT || '131072'); // 128K\n    this.checkIntervalMs = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_CHECK_INTERVAL || '30000');\n    this.cooldownSec = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_COOLDOWN_SEC || '120');\n    \n    this.messages = [];\n    this.totalChars = 0;\n    this.lastSummarize = 0;\n    this.backupDir = path.join(os.tmpdir(), 'openclaw', 'history_backup');\n    this.periodicInterval = null; // 保存定时器ID\n    this.ensureBackupDir();\n    \n    this.startPeriodicCheck();\n  }\n\n  ensureBackupDir() {\n    if (!fs.existsSync(this.backupDir)) {\n      fs.mkdirSync(this.backupDir, { recursive: true });\n    }\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 估算 token（轻量方法）\n   */\n  estimateTokens(text) {\n    const chinese = (text.match(/[\\u4e00-\\u9fa5]/g) || []).length;\n    const other = text.length - chinese;\n    return Math.ceil(chinese / 1.5 + other / 4);\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 从底层获取真实使用率\n\n=== Protection middleware ==="}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":197,"aggregated":"=== Protection 模块 ===\n/**\n * OpenCLaw 保护层 - 上下文保护模块 (context_protector.js)\n * \n * 功能：\n * - 多维度检测（消息数+字符数+Token使用率）\n * - 自动压缩（API优先，降级裁剪）\n * - 定期轮询底层检测\n * - 回滚机制\n */\n\nimport * as fs from 'fs';\nimport * as path from 'path';\nimport * as os from 'os';\n\nclass ContextProtector {\n  constructor(options = {}) {\n    this.msgThreshold = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_MSG_THRESHOLD || '50');\n    this.charThreshold = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_CHAR_THRESHOLD || '102400'); // 100KB\n    this.tokenRatioThreshold = parseFloat(process.env.OPENCLAW_TOKEN_RATIO || '0.8');\n    this.tokenLimit = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_TOKEN_LIMIT || '131072'); // 128K\n    this.checkIntervalMs = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_CHECK_INTERVAL || '30000');\n    this.cooldownSec = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_COOLDOWN_SEC || '120');\n    \n    this.messages = [];\n    this.totalChars = 0;\n    this.lastSummarize = 0;\n    this.backupDir = path.join(os.tmpdir(), 'openclaw', 'history_backup');\n    this.periodicInterval = null; // 保存定时器ID\n    this.ensureBackupDir();\n    \n    this.startPeriodicCheck();\n  }\n\n  ensureBackupDir() {\n    if (!fs.existsSync(this.backupDir)) {\n      fs.mkdirSync(this.backupDir, { recursive: true });\n    }\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 估算 token（轻量方法）\n   */\n  estimateTokens(text) {\n    const chinese = (text.match(/[\\u4e00-\\u9fa5]/g) || []).length;\n    const other = text.length - chinese;\n    return Math.ceil(chinese / 1.5 + other / 4);\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 从底层获取真实使用率\n\n=== Protection middleware ===","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776442548852}}
{"type":"message","id":"3d411672","parentId":"0f31a3b5","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:15:53.281Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. The context management system is split into TWO implementations:\n\n1. **v8 built-in** (`~/.openclaw/v8/src/context/ContextProtector.js`) - minimal, just token estimation + simple truncation\n2. **Protection module** (`~/.openclaw/protection/`) - a more sophisticated multi-dimensional protector with:\n   - Message count threshold (50)\n   - Character threshold (100KB)\n   - Token ratio threshold (0.8)\n   - Token limit (128K)\n   - Periodic polling\n   - Backup rollback mechanism\n   - Auto-summarization\n\nLet me check the protection module more thoroughly.","thinkingSignature":"3413b123982b70cdb3480db1e63c6d297e123fd3b138bedcedf554cc61f13630"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8ic47k0b0z3m_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== Protection 完整检测逻辑 ===\"\ngrep -A 30 \"protect\\|truncat\\|summar\" ~/.openclaw/protection/context_protector.js 2>/dev/null | head -60\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Protection 中间件 ===\"\ncat ~/.openclaw/protection/middleware.js 2>/dev/null | head -50"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":90549,"output":232,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112419,"cost":{"input":0.0271647,"output":0.0002784,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02874138}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776442548927,"responseId":"06318fb30123ad45c46cdae237551b79"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0700df5c","parentId":"3d411672","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:15:53.735Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_8ic47k0b0z3m_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== Protection 完整检测逻辑 ===\n * OpenCLaw 保护层 - 上下文保护模块 (context_protector.js)\n * \n * 功能：\n * - 多维度检测（消息数+字符数+Token使用率）\n * - 自动压缩（API优先，降级裁剪）\n * - 定期轮询底层检测\n * - 回滚机制\n */\n\nimport * as fs from 'fs';\nimport * as path from 'path';\nimport * as os from 'os';\n\nclass ContextProtector {\n  constructor(options = {}) {\n    this.msgThreshold = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_MSG_THRESHOLD || '50');\n    this.charThreshold = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_CHAR_THRESHOLD || '102400'); // 100KB\n    this.tokenRatioThreshold = parseFloat(process.env.OPENCLAW_TOKEN_RATIO || '0.8');\n    this.tokenLimit = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_TOKEN_LIMIT || '131072'); // 128K\n    this.checkIntervalMs = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_CHECK_INTERVAL || '30000');\n    this.cooldownSec = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_COOLDOWN_SEC || '120');\n    \n    this.messages = [];\n    this.totalChars = 0;\n    this.lastSummarize = 0;\n    this.backupDir = path.join(os.tmpdir(), 'openclaw', 'history_backup');\n    this.periodicInterval = null; // 保存定时器ID\n    this.ensureBackupDir();\n    \n    this.startPeriodicCheck();\n  }\n--\n      let summary = null;\n      \n      // 优先调用外部 API\n      // if (typeof summarizeAPI === 'function') {\n      //   summary = await summarizeAPI(this.messages.slice(0, -5));\n      // }\n      \n      // 模拟摘要生成（实际应调用 API）\n      if (!summary) {\n        const recent = this.messages.slice(-10);\n        summary = `[会话摘要] 共 ${this.messages.length} 条消息，关键内容: ${recent.map(m => m.content?.slice(0, 50)).join(' | ')}`;\n      }\n\n      this.messages = [\n        { role: 'system', content: `[历史摘要] ${summary}` },\n        ...this.messages.slice(-5)\n      ];\n      \n      this.recalcChars();\n      this.lastSummarize = Date.now();\n      \n      return { success: true, reason, oldCount: this.messages.length + 5, newCount: this.messages.length };\n      \n    } catch (err) {\n      // 降级：保留最近20条 + 关键信息\n      const critical = this.extractCriticalInfo();\n      const kept = this.messages.slice(-20);\n      kept.unshift({ role: 'system', content: `[关键信息] ${critical}` });\n\n=== Protection 中间件 ===\n/**\n * OpenClaw 上下文中间件 - 反向代理版本 v2.0\n * \n * 拦截 Webhook 请求，转发给 Gateway，同时调用上下文保护层\n * \n * 工作流程:\n * 用户 → POST /webhook → 中间件 → 转发 Gateway\n *                          ↓\n *                    异步调用保护层\n */\n\nimport { createServer } from 'http';\nimport { contextProtector } from './context_protector.js';\nimport { securityGate } from './security_gate.js';\n\nconst PORT = parseInt(process.env.MIDDLEWARE_PORT || '3002');\nconst GATEWAY_URL = process.env.OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_URL || 'http://127.0.0.1:18789';\nconst CONTEXT_TIMEOUT_MS = parseInt(process.env.CONTEXT_TIMEOUT_MS || '2000');\n\nconst server = createServer(async (req, res) => {\n  // CORS\n  res.setHeader('Access-Control-Allow-Origin', '*');\n  res.setHeader('Access-Control-Allow-Methods', 'GET, POST, OPTIONS');\n  res.setHeader('Access-Control-Allow-Headers', 'Content-Type, Authorization');\n  \n  if (req.method === 'OPTIONS') {\n    res.writeHead(200);\n    res.end();\n    return;\n  }\n\n  // 健康检查\n  if (req.url === '/health') {\n    res.writeHead(200, { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' });\n    res.end(JSON.stringify({ status: 'ok', timestamp: Date.now(), service: 'middleware' }));\n    return;\n  }\n\n  // Webhook 拦截\n  if (req.url === '/webhook' && req.method === 'POST') {\n    try {\n      let body = '';\n      for await (const chunk of req) {\n        body += chunk;\n      }\n      \n      let data;\n      try {\n        data = JSON.parse(body);\n      } catch {"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":231,"aggregated":"=== Protection 完整检测逻辑 ===\n * OpenCLaw 保护层 - 上下文保护模块 (context_protector.js)\n * \n * 功能：\n * - 多维度检测（消息数+字符数+Token使用率）\n * - 自动压缩（API优先，降级裁剪）\n * - 定期轮询底层检测\n * - 回滚机制\n */\n\nimport * as fs from 'fs';\nimport * as path from 'path';\nimport * as os from 'os';\n\nclass ContextProtector {\n  constructor(options = {}) {\n    this.msgThreshold = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_MSG_THRESHOLD || '50');\n    this.charThreshold = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_CHAR_THRESHOLD || '102400'); // 100KB\n    this.tokenRatioThreshold = parseFloat(process.env.OPENCLAW_TOKEN_RATIO || '0.8');\n    this.tokenLimit = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_TOKEN_LIMIT || '131072'); // 128K\n    this.checkIntervalMs = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_CHECK_INTERVAL || '30000');\n    this.cooldownSec = parseInt(process.env.OPENCLAW_COOLDOWN_SEC || '120');\n    \n    this.messages = [];\n    this.totalChars = 0;\n    this.lastSummarize = 0;\n    this.backupDir = path.join(os.tmpdir(), 'openclaw', 'history_backup');\n    this.periodicInterval = null; // 保存定时器ID\n    this.ensureBackupDir();\n    \n    this.startPeriodicCheck();\n  }\n--\n      let summary = null;\n      \n      // 优先调用外部 API\n      // if (typeof summarizeAPI === 'function') {\n      //   summary = await summarizeAPI(this.messages.slice(0, -5));\n      // }\n      \n      // 模拟摘要生成（实际应调用 API）\n      if (!summary) {\n        const recent = this.messages.slice(-10);\n        summary = `[会话摘要] 共 ${this.messages.length} 条消息，关键内容: ${recent.map(m => m.content?.slice(0, 50)).join(' | ')}`;\n      }\n\n      this.messages = [\n        { role: 'system', content: `[历史摘要] ${summary}` },\n        ...this.messages.slice(-5)\n      ];\n      \n      this.recalcChars();\n      this.lastSummarize = Date.now();\n      \n      return { success: true, reason, oldCount: this.messages.length + 5, newCount: this.messages.length };\n      \n    } catch (err) {\n      // 降级：保留最近20条 + 关键信息\n      const critical = this.extractCriticalInfo();\n      const kept = this.messages.slice(-20);\n      kept.unshift({ role: 'system', content: `[关键信息] ${critical}` });\n\n=== Protection 中间件 ===\n/**\n * OpenClaw 上下文中间件 - 反向代理版本 v2.0\n * \n * 拦截 Webhook 请求，转发给 Gateway，同时调用上下文保护层\n * \n * 工作流程:\n * 用户 → POST /webhook → 中间件 → 转发 Gateway\n *                          ↓\n *                    异步调用保护层\n */\n\nimport { createServer } from 'http';\nimport { contextProtector } from './context_protector.js';\nimport { securityGate } from './security_gate.js';\n\nconst PORT = parseInt(process.env.MIDDLEWARE_PORT || '3002');\nconst GATEWAY_URL = process.env.OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_URL || 'http://127.0.0.1:18789';\nconst CONTEXT_TIMEOUT_MS = parseInt(process.env.CONTEXT_TIMEOUT_MS || '2000');\n\nconst server = createServer(async (req, res) => {\n  // CORS\n  res.setHeader('Access-Control-Allow-Origin', '*');\n  res.setHeader('Access-Control-Allow-Methods', 'GET, POST, OPTIONS');\n  res.setHeader('Access-Control-Allow-Headers', 'Content-Type, Authorization');\n  \n  if (req.method === 'OPTIONS') {\n    res.writeHead(200);\n    res.end();\n    return;\n  }\n\n  // 健康检查\n  if (req.url === '/health') {\n    res.writeHead(200, { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' });\n    res.end(JSON.stringify({ status: 'ok', timestamp: Date.now(), service: 'middleware' }));\n    return;\n  }\n\n  // Webhook 拦截\n  if (req.url === '/webhook' && req.method === 'POST') {\n    try {\n      let body = '';\n      for await (const chunk of req) {\n        body += chunk;\n      }\n      \n      let data;\n      try {\n        data = JSON.parse(body);\n      } catch {","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776442553644}}
{"type":"message","id":"049f25c8","parentId":"0700df5c","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:16:03.822Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a very clear picture of the context management system. It's actually quite sophisticated - there are TWO protection systems:\n\n1. **Protection module** (`~/.openclaw/protection/`) - a standalone Node.js middleware that:\n   - Monitors message count, character count, and token ratio\n   - Has periodic checks (30s interval)\n   - Auto-summarizes when thresholds are exceeded\n   - Has backup/rollback mechanism\n   - Is deployed as a separate HTTP service on port 3002\n\n2. **v8 built-in ContextProtector** (`~/.openclaw/v8/src/context/ContextProtector.js`) - a minimal built-in that:\n   - Does basic token estimation\n   - Has a simple threshold-based summarization\n\nThe protection module is more complete. But wait - is it actually running? Let me check if the protection middleware is actually running.","thinkingSignature":"c04bed1ed76508f16dcf010371fc08c9a47b011fe83ec791b037f22ed6961bea"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fblsywbtbvyi_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== Protection 服务状态 ===\"\nps aux 2>/dev/null | grep -E \"protection|middleware|context\" | grep -v grep | head -5\n\necho \"\"\nss -tlnp 2>/dev/null | grep -E \"3002|3101|3106\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Protection 端口监听 ===\"\ncurl -s --connect-timeout 2 http://localhost:3002/health 2>/dev/null || echo \"3002 未监听\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== context-protector 实际使用 ===\"\ngrep -r \"contextProtector\\|protectContext\\|ContextProtector\" ~/.openclaw/v8/src/index.js 2>/dev/null | head -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":91772,"output":352,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113762,"cost":{"input":0.0275316,"output":0.00042239999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02925228}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776442553738,"res