{"type":"message","id":"12a91d51","parentId":"176e626a","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:16:18.946Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Very interesting findings:\n\n1. **Protection middleware (port 3002) is NOT running** - it was coded but never deployed as a service\n2. **The v8 built-in ContextProtector exists but isn't actually integrated** into the Gateway's context assembly flow3. **The protection module is standalone** and not connected to the actual Gateway\n\nThis means the sophisticated protection layer (multi-dimensional monitoring, auto-summarization, backup/rollback) is completely disconnected from the running system.\n\nThe actual context management in the running system is:\n- Basic token estimation (simple char/4 for English, char/1.5 for Chinese)- When token count > 80% of maxContextTokens (128K), trigger a simple truncation\n\n\n- No real API-based summarization, just basic message retention\n\nLet me verify whether the Gateway actually has access to the ContextProtector at all.","thinkingSignature":"df98093478a748d6557442988e0086af79e3dce40f38c5fffe2dca7d80852895"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3gdio39yqpj4_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== Gateway 上下文相关配置 ===\"\ncat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | python3 -c \"\nimport json,sys\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\nctx = d.get('context',{})\nprint(json.dumps(ctx, indent=2))\n\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== ContextProtector 在 Gateway 中使用情况 ===\"\ngrep -r \"ContextProtector\\|context.*protect\\|protectContext\" ~/.openclaw/v8/src/ --include=\"*.js\" 2>/dev/null | grep -v \".js.map\" | grep -v \"node_modules\" | grep -v \"ContextProtector.js\" | head -10\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 实际上下文限制配置 ===\"\ncat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | python3 -c \"\nimport json,sys\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\nmodels = d.get('models',{})\nfor m in models.get('providers',{}).get('minimax',{}).get('models',[]):\n    if isinstance(m,dict) and 'contextWindow' in str(m):\n        print(m)\n\" 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":93556,"output":433,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115627,"cost":{"input":0.0280668,"output":0.0005195999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.029884679999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776442564261,"responseId":"06318fc37d2c647ebb64ae033dbb0bfd"}}
{"type":"message","id":"df2b02fa","parentId":"12a91d51","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:16:19.473Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3gdio39yqpj4_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== Gateway 上下文相关配置 ===\n{}\n\n=== ContextProtector 在 Gateway 中使用情况 ===\n\n=== 实际上下文限制配置 ===\n{'id': 'MiniMax-M2.7', 'name': 'MiniMax M2.7', 'reasoning': True, 'input': ['text', 'image'], 'cost': {'input': 0.3, 'output': 1.2, 'cacheRead': 0.06, 'cacheWrite': 0.375}, 'contextWindow': 204800, 'maxTokens': 131072}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":227,"aggregated":"=== Gateway 上下文相关配置 ===\n{}\n\n=== ContextProtector 在 Gateway 中使用情况 ===\n\n=== 实际上下文限制配置 ===\n{'id': 'MiniMax-M2.7', 'name': 'MiniMax M2.7', 'reasoning': True, 'input': ['text', 'image'], 'cost': {'input': 0.3, 'output': 1.2, 'cacheRead': 0.06, 'cacheWrite': 0.375}, 'contextWindow': 204800, 'maxTokens': 131072}","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776442579384}}
{"type":"message","id":"5d88e57b","parentId":"df2b02fa","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:16:39.718Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now the picture is very clear. The context management system has a severe gap:\n\n**What's deployed:**\n1. v8 built-in ContextProtector (exists as code but NOT integrated into Gateway)\n2. Protection module in `~/.openclaw/protection/` (sophisticated but NOT running - port 3002 not listening)\n3. No real context management config in openclaw.json (empty `{}`)\n4. Model has contextWindow: 204800 tokens for MiniMax-M2.7\n\n**What actually happens:**\n- No active context protection at the Gateway level\n- Compaction mode: \"safeguard\" - but what does it actually do?\n\n\n- Session history gets sent as-is to the LLM with no active truncation or summarization kicking in\n- The built-in ContextProtector code is never actually invoked anywhere\n\nSo the Context Engine as described in the v2026.4.14 documentation—with its four lifecycle nodes and pluggable architecture—isn't implemented at all. What I have instead is a model with a 204800 token context window and a \"safeguard\" compaction mode, but no active enforcement of those limits.\n\nLooking deeper, there's a protection module that was written but never connected to the Gateway, and even if it were, it relies on a summarizeAPI that would need an external LLM call. There's no usage tracking either. So the real situation is that the system depends entirely on the model's native context window limit and whatever \"safeguard\" mode is supposed to do—neither of which has any active enforcement behind it.","thinkingSignature":"905ae1690314452eba802bf50c3e89b8c08bad0dd79bba12d131f2f6c1798cdb"},{"type":"text","text":"## 上下文管理深度分析\n\n---\n\n### 实际情况\n\n**Context Engine 四节点生命周期——文档描述 vs 实际部署**：\n\n```\n文档架构：\n  Ingest → Assemble → Compact → After Turn\n              ↓\n  可插拔 Context Engine（内置 legacy，可替换）\n\n实际系统：\n  Assemble（消息拼装）→ 发给 LLM → 无主动压缩\n              ↓\n  无任何活跃的上下文管理器\n```\n\n---\n\n### 三套 Context 相关代码\n\n| 代码 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `v8/src/context/ContextProtector.js` | ❌ 未集成 | 存在代码但 Gateway 未调用 |\n| `protection/context_protector.js` | ❌ 未运行 | 复杂保护层（port 3002），从未启动 |\n| `protection/middleware.js` | ❌ 未运行 | HTTP 中间件，未部署 |\n| `Compaction (mode=safeguard)` | ⚠️ 被动触发 | 行为不明确 |\n\n---\n\n### 真实上下文行为\n\n```\n你发送消息\n    ↓\n消息追加到 session history\n    ↓\nsession history 完整发送给 LLM（无主动截断）\n    ↓\nLLM 自己根据 contextWindow 截断（模型行为，非系统行为）\n```\n\n**只有这些限制**：\n- MiniMax-M2.7: contextWindow = 204800 tokens\n- Compaction mode = \"safeguard\"（含义不明，未查到源码）\n- Gateway 配置中 `context: {}`（空对象）\n\n---\n\n### 保护层（已编码但未运行）\n\n`~/.openclaw/protection/` 中的模块原本设计用来：\n- 每 30 秒轮询检测消息数/字符数/token使用率\n- 超过阈值自动摘要\n- 备份 + 回滚机制\n- 调用外部 API 摘要\n\n但 port 3002 未监听，这些都没接上。\n\n---\n\n### 结论\n\n| 项目 | 评估 |\n|------|------|\n| Context Engine 文档 | 架构存在但未实现 |\n| 实际上下文管理 | **纯模型侧截断**（contextWindow 204800） |\n| 主动压缩/摘要 | ❌ 不存在 |\n| 多维度监控 | ❌ 未运行 |\n| 用量追踪 | ❌ 未配置 |\n| 备份/回滚 | ❌ 未激活 |\n\n**当前是\"信任模型上下文窗口\"模式，没有系统级的上下文保护。**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":94119,"output":826,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116583,"cost":{"input":0.0282357,"output":0.0009912,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03052518}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776442579476,"responseId":"06318fd1d8475958493f580bb22eac6f"}}
