{"type":"message","id":"94499a55","parentId":"5f076e6c","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:42:20.571Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想了解\"接受多说一句的妥协\"具体是什么意思。简单解释一下。","thinkingSignature":"9519fe5346092305b4f33c3266e29867a7ed5cc34483b3e38a303e6d96b434ef"},{"type":"text","text":"意思是：\n\n**Hook 派发 subagent 后，主 Agent 还是会被触发。**\n\n它看到 marker 或 spawn 成功的通知，然后输出：\n\n```\n[系统] 任务已派发给子 Agent，请等待执行结果。\n```\n\n这就是\"多说的一句\"。\n\n---\n\n**对比**：\n\n| 方案 | 用户看到的 |\n|------|-----------|\n| 理想（静默派发） | 直接看到子 Agent 的代码结果 |\n| 妥协（多说一句） | 先看到\"任务已派发\" → 然后才是子 Agent 的结果 |\n\n两句话，不是只有一句。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":136,"cacheRead":136062,"cacheWrite":263,"totalTokens":136519,"cost":{"input":0.0000174,"output":0.00016319999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00816372,"cacheWrite":0.000098625,"total":0.008442944999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776444128695,"responseId":"063195df5805cb7926359b48dd1d87c7"}}
