{"type":"message","id":"dc4cfdcb","parentId":"b5577230","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:53:17.956Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking how to send a test message with the [AUTO_ROUTE] tag to the agent. This is a practical question about testing. I can just send a message directly right now as the main agent. The test is simple: send \"[AUTO_ROUTE]\" prefixed message and observe what the agent does.\n\nBut wait - I need to be careful. The AUTO_ROUTE marker would only work if SOUL.md has the rule. Since we haven't added any rule to SOUL.md yet, the test would just show that the agent ignores the marker and responds normally.\n\nThe user's question is \"how to send\" - literally, how to get a message with this tag to the agent. As the main agent, I can just send a message right now in this session. \n\nI should send a test message with the [AUTO_ROUTE] tag to see how the agent responds when it encounters this marker.","thinkingSignature":"655114d8c1f4655ba18d171047cf342cd6b407e0b7b4216d78d7d3f9a1d11a74"},{"type":"text","text":"直接发：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8vrs319llj5a_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"[AUTO_ROUTE] 这是一条测试消息，帮我写一个Python快速排序\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":233,"cacheRead":141166,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":141399,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0.00027959999999999997,"cacheRead":0.008469959999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.008749559999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776444789319,"responseId":"0631987444c5fa940a67f59beaca8416"}}
